<figureCitation box="[469,577,1668,1694]" captionStart="Figure 14" captionStartId="17.[160,227,1388,1411]" captionTargetBox="[168,1147,145,1355]" captionTargetId="figure-89@17.[166,1149,142,1357]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Figure 14. Geographic distribution maps. (a) Tetragus species; (b) Gibboryctes species; (c) Heterogomphus gracilicornis Prell." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6758347" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6758347/files/figure.png" pageId="30" pageNumber="220">Figure 14</figureCitation>
(a))
</emphasis>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
